These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, japanese, french, russian
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, billiard, domino
City: new-york, rome, boston, berlin
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, february, january
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, rose, begonia, orchid
House: modern, cottage, ranch-style, craftsman
There 4 different types of food: radish, garlic, tomato, pear
 1. the indonesian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person eating radish is the japanese##1
 7. the cottage house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person eating pear is the person who growsrose##1
10. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
11. the modern house is the japanese##1
12. the person eating garlic is the person who growsbegonia##1
13. the craftsman house is on the right of the russian##1
14. the cottage house is the russian##1
15. the craftsman house is the person traveling to boston##1
16. the indonesian is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
17. the french is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Nationality      | indonesian       | russian      | french       | japanese    |
| Game         | monopoly    | domino    | scrabble      | billiard    |
| City           | berlin | new-york       | boston | rome     |
| Birthday   | april         | february  | january      | june     |
| Flower   | rose          | orchid     | begonia       | bellflower |
| House         | ranch-style       | cottage | craftsman       | modern   |
| Food     | pear     | tomato  | garlic         | radish   |

