.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
City: marseilles, rome, miami, nizza
4 different games are played: snooker, poker, bridge, billiard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, bellflower, rose
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, badminton, golf, climbing
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, tower, cape-cod
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, milk, hot-chocolate
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, may, february, april
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who growsiris##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
16. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
17. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| City          | miami     | rome     | marseilles      | nizza  |
| Game         | billiard  | snooker  | bridge      | poker |
| Flower   | rose   | bellflower     | marigold | iris        |
| Sport   | soccer    | badminton        | golf        | climbing        |
| House   | tower | gothic-revival | cape-cod   | ranch-style  |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk       | fanta        | milk       |
| Birthday     | august     | february     | april       | may     |

