City: san-francisco, hannover, edinburgh, venice
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, boat, skateboard
4 different games are played: bridge, go, snooker, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, cola, almond-milk
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the russian##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the egyptian##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
10. the person playing poker is the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person playing poker##1
13. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
14. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
15. the german is the person driving the skateboard##1
16. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
17. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |     3     |      4      |
