4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, dunhill, montecristo, game
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, green, turquise, orange
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person who likes green is the bolivar-smoker##1
