 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is the musician##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
12. the project-manager is the montecristo-smoker##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
14. the musician is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsbegonia##1
16. the police-officer is on the far right##1
17. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
